commit 4c3c07e09187bb7c73177a7d802b158a6aa6f1a2
Author: luxgrain <luxgrain@users.noreply.github.com>
Date:   Thu Apr 23 05:47:04 2026 +0900

    iop: add GALOSH-YUV post-demosaic sRGB denoiser
    
    New IOP galosh_yuv running between demosaic and denoiseprofile in the
    RAW pipeline (priority 8.5f in v30/v50 order, 9.5f in legacy, 28.0f in
    jpg orders alongside the linear-RGB cluster).
    
    The module wraps galosh_yuv_denoise_srgb (extracted into galosh_yuv.h):
    linear Y-GAT + 2-pass WHT-LOSH on luma + Y-guided LOESS chroma
    regression, blind sigma estimation when alpha/sigma_sq are 0.
    
    Params: strength_y, strength_c (0..4, default 1.0), alpha, sigma_sq
    (0 => blind).  RGBA->planar RGB unpack around the denoiser, alpha
    passes through.
    
    Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>

